description: Cancels retrieval of a virtual tape from the virtual tape shelf (VTS) to a gateway after the retrieval process is initiated. The virtual tape is returned to the VTS. This operation is only supported in the tape gateway type.

parameters.name: GatewayARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the gateway. Use the  ListGateways operation to return a list of gateways for your account and Amazon Web Services Region.

parameters.name: TapeARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the virtual tape you want to cancel retrieval for.

nested_items.name: TapeARN
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the virtual tape for which retrieval was canceled.
